sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Admin/User
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Operator as TrustyAI Operator<br/>Controller
    participant ExternalUser as External User
    participant Router as OpenShift Router<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.3
    participant OAuthProxy as OAuth Proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant OAuth as OpenShift OAuth Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant TrustyAI as TrustyAI Service<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus
    participant KServe as KServe InferenceService
    participant Database as Database<br/>3306/5432 JDBC

    Note over User,Database: Flow 1: TrustyAI Service Deployment
    User->>K8sAPI: Create TrustyAIService CR<br/>Bearer Token Auth
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: Watch event (CR created)
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Deployment<br/>SA Bearer Token
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Services<br/>SA Bearer Token
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Route<br/>SA Bearer Token
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create ServiceMonitor<br/>SA Bearer Token

    Note over ExternalUser,TrustyAI: Flow 2: External User Access via Route
    ExternalUser->>Router: HTTPS Request<br/>443/TCP TLS1.3
    Router->>OAuthProxy: Forward (re-encrypt)<br/>443/TCP TLS1.2+
    OAuthProxy->>OAuth: Validate Token<br/>OAuth 2.0 Flow
    OAuth-->>OAuthProxy: Token Valid
    OAuthProxy->>TrustyAI: Forward Request<br/>8080/TCP HTTP (localhost)
    TrustyAI-->>OAuthProxy: Response
    OAuthProxy-->>Router: Response (TLS)
    Router-->>ExternalUser: Response (TLS)

    Note over Prometheus,TrustyAI: Flow 3: Prometheus Metrics Scraping
    Prometheus->>TrustyAI: GET /q/metrics<br/>80/TCP HTTP
    TrustyAI-->>Prometheus: Metrics (trustyai_spd, trustyai_dir)

    Note over Operator,KServe: Flow 4: KServe InferenceService Integration
    Operator->>K8sAPI: List InferenceServices<br/>SA Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: InferenceService List
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Patch Deployment<br/>Inject MM_PAYLOAD_PROCESSORS
    KServe->>TrustyAI: Send Inference Payloads<br/>443/TCP HTTPS Service Cert

    Note over TrustyAI,Database: Flow 5: Database Storage (Optional)
    TrustyAI->>Database: Store Inference Data<br/>JDBC TLS1.2+ (optional)<br/>DB Credentials
    Database-->>TrustyAI: Acknowledgment
